// Man page for compare
manCompare="COMPARE(1)                       X Shell Manual                       COMPARE(1)

<b>NAME</b>
    compare - Compare two numbers
<b>SYNOPSIS</b>
    <b>compare NUMBER1 NUMBER2</b>
<b>DESCRIPTION</b>
    Compare two numeric values and determine which is greater.
<b>EXAMPLE:</b>
    <b>compare 100 50</b>
    Compare 100 vs 50

    <b>compare 42 42</b>
    Compare equal values

    <b>compare 3.14 2.71</b>
    Compare decimals"